article.headline: Alcorn State 77, Alabama State 70
article.story: LORMAN, Miss. (AP) -- Brian Jackson had 22 points and six rebounds to lead Alcorn State to a 77-70 victory over Alabama State on Saturday. Alcorn State (4-10, 3-4 Southwestern Athletic Conference) led by seven at the half, 40-33. DeAndre Jones added 13 for the Braves and Dion Callans had 12. For Alabama State (4-11, 1-5) Malcolm Campbell and Alexander Oliver had 15 points each.
